## 👀 Releases

#ChainIDE for Astar: Development Game Changer

The integration of Astar Network with ChainIDE will advance your development experience on Astar Substrate.

Here's what ChainIDE brings to your developer toolkit:

- 🖥️ **Easy Start**: Open ChainIDE in your browser and start building smart contracts right away.
- 📘 **Rich Learning Resources**: Access a wide range of tutorials and examples, perfect for all skill levels, plus benefit from ready-to-use templates.
- ⚙️ **Intuitive Development Process**: Enjoy a user-friendly environment for writing, compiling, debugging, testing, deploying, and verifying your contracts.
- 🔍 **Effortless Debugging**: With an interactive compiler and interaction module, tackle coding challenges head-on.
- 🚀 **Deployment & Interaction Made Easy**: Deploy and interact with your smart contracts seamlessly.
- ✅ **Simple Verification Process**: Verify your contracts in just a few clicks and view them on BlockScout scan.

Astar ChainIDE is not just about easing the development process; it's about opening doors to limitless possibilities in the ecosystem.
Read more in the Astar Blog [article](https://astar.network/blog/chainide-for-astar:-development-game-changer-40331) and enhance your development experience with Astar ChainIDE for [EVM](https://chainide.com/s/createTempProject/astar-evm?language=en) and [Wasm](https://chainide.com/s/createTempProject/astar-wasm?language=en)!

